title: DEPARTMENT SUPPORT TECHNICIAN $16.67 - $20.36/hr. The (pic)
text: $16.67 - $20.36/hr. The Community Resource Agency is seeking a Department Support Tech to perform technical and para-professional work involved in completing the professional functions of the agency; to prepare statistical and technical reports; and to preform related duties as assigned. HS Diploma or GED supplemented by college level coursework and 2 years of responsible support experience required. Apply online at www.tuolumnecounty.ca.gov Closes: 11/4/2015
